  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a medium bowl, whisk together almond milk, almond flour, coconut oil, maple syrup, vanilla extract, ground ginger, ground cinnamon, and salt until smooth.",
    "Stir in the blanched almonds and chopped fresh ginger.",
    "Pour the mixture into a greased 8-inch round baking dish.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes, or until the edges are lightly golden brown.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for 5 minutes.",
    "Drizzle with fresh lemon juice and serve warm."
  ],
